00:12:35.632 --> 00:12:40.162
Whatever the reason for this rupture, this break, it didn’t stop

00:12:40.232 --> 00:12:45.152
Carroll from carrying out Alice’s wish, and putting her story to paper.

00:12:45.952 --> 00:12:49.482
He continued to write out the stories and intended to give

00:12:49.502 --> 00:12:53.692
