00:14:06.387 --> 00:14:10.247
In the story, Carroll also included much inspiration

00:14:10.277 --> 00:14:13.697
from his academic career, and interest in maths.

00:14:14.307 --> 00:14:20.467
You may remember that the story is full of absurd logic and riddles, puzzles to solve.

00:14:21.657 --> 00:14:27.707
