00:14:59.587 --> 00:15:04.317
making fun of new concepts in symbolic algebra that he opposed.

00:15:05.117 --> 00:15:08.867
Clearly, it was a wonderful story for Caroll and the girls,

00:15:08.977 --> 00:15:11.977
